long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing SearchSwiftly - your gateway to streamlined browsing on Chrome. Say goodbye to endless search results and hello to efficiency. With SearchSwiftly, experience lightning-fast searches, precise results, and effortless navigation. Simplify your online experience today and unlock the power of seamless browsing with SearchSwiftly.

By clicking “Add to Chrome”, you accept and agree to install the SearchSwiftly extension, set the Chrome™ default search to SearchSwiftly, and to the Terms of Use, and Privacy Policy.

Terms of Use: https://www.searchswiftly.online/terms-of-use
Privacy Policy: https://www.searchswiftly.online/privacy-policy
